WEBVTT

01:30.930 --> 01:35.020
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.600 --> 01:39.460
[2024]

02:04.920 --> 02:06.580
Xia Xiaolan, you must be home.

02:06.840 --> 02:09.169
Have the business trip field study report

02:09.310 --> 02:10.560
ready for me

02:10.750 --> 02:11.750
by 10 AM tomorrow.

02:12.800 --> 02:14.190
Home isn't a container,

02:14.910 --> 02:16.040
but a relationship.

02:17.030 --> 02:18.910
We think it will last forever,

02:19.710 --> 02:21.400
but at some stage in life,

02:21.630 --> 02:22.420
we lose it.

02:24.150 --> 02:25.010
Starting then,

02:25.960 --> 02:26.710
going home

02:27.579 --> 02:29.350
becomes a new life lesson.

02:32.329 --> 02:34.670
[Episode 6: What Is a Home?]

02:35.750 --> 02:36.560
Actually, I think

02:36.560 --> 02:37.680
today went well.

02:38.400 --> 02:39.470
You paid her back.

02:39.870 --> 02:41.870
You don't owe her anything anymore.

03:05.680 --> 03:07.010
Come on down, comrades.

03:14.280 --> 03:15.080
Sorry. Sorry.

03:15.470 --> 03:16.470
Please excuse me.

03:17.680 --> 03:18.640
These three

03:18.870 --> 03:20.190
were sent by the county

03:20.470 --> 03:22.400
as agriculture technical guides.

03:22.630 --> 03:24.240
Let's give them a warm welcome.

03:24.240 --> 03:25.000
Amazing!

03:25.750 --> 03:26.470
Great!

03:26.590 --> 03:27.150
Welcome.

03:29.120 --> 03:30.470
Hello everyone, I'm Yang Jiancong.

03:30.470 --> 03:31.520
I'm from Guangdong.

03:31.520 --> 03:32.560
Welcome.

03:33.840 --> 03:34.560
Hello everyone.

03:34.560 --> 03:35.710
I'm Wang Jianhua

03:35.810 --> 03:36.810
from the capital.

03:36.840 --> 03:37.360
I hope

03:37.430 --> 03:38.680
I can be of help to you all.

03:38.680 --> 03:39.280
Great!

03:39.310 --> 03:40.630
Welcome.

03:43.000 --> 03:43.840
I'm Tan Xihao.

03:44.030 --> 03:45.030
I'm from Jiangxi.

03:45.400 --> 03:46.470
Good!

03:48.680 --> 03:49.480
In the future,

03:49.910 --> 03:50.590
if anyone has

03:50.590 --> 03:52.030
questions about agriculture,

03:52.030 --> 03:53.030
you can ask them.

03:54.960 --> 03:55.800
That's great.

03:57.170 --> 03:58.370
Comrade Xia Xiaolan,

03:59.079 --> 04:00.940
I hope this letter finds you well.

04:01.470 --> 04:02.360
It's been over 3 months

04:02.360 --> 04:03.590
since we met.

04:04.590 --> 04:07.050
I have some thoughts
I want to share with you.

04:08.190 --> 04:10.520
I still remember
the first day I came here;

04:10.870 --> 04:12.590
the first person I saw

04:13.280 --> 04:14.030
was you.

04:16.040 --> 04:17.120
Since then,

04:18.120 --> 04:20.560
I have believed in fate.

04:55.190 --> 04:56.760
[To: Xia Xiaolan]

05:38.120 --> 05:39.159
Someone is up late,

05:39.159 --> 05:41.090
trying to steal the Door God's job.

05:42.070 --> 05:43.600
What are you talking about?

05:44.510 --> 05:45.040
Listen.

05:45.870 --> 05:47.130
Your uncle is amazing.

05:48.430 --> 05:49.630
Tao isn't bad either.

05:52.070 --> 05:53.070
Tell me the truth.

05:53.950 --> 05:55.240
Just now at dinner,

05:55.680 --> 05:57.040
did you pray to God

05:57.070 --> 05:57.750
for rain?

05:59.680 --> 06:01.010
I swear to Chairman Mao.

06:01.360 --> 06:03.020
This has nothing to do with me.

06:05.190 --> 06:05.720
Fine.

06:06.870 --> 06:07.960
Since you can't sleep,

06:07.960 --> 06:09.560
let me share a story with you.

06:12.130 --> 06:13.720
Otherwise, if I read it alone,

06:13.720 --> 06:15.210
you might think I rejected you

06:15.210 --> 06:17.070
because I can't let go of the past.

06:23.870 --> 06:25.160
Comrade Xia Xiaolan,

06:25.830 --> 06:27.690
I hope this letter finds you well.

06:28.240 --> 06:29.160
It's been over 3 months

06:29.160 --> 06:30.510
since we met.

06:31.310 --> 06:33.480
I have some thoughts to share with you.

06:34.120 --> 06:36.450
I still remember
the first day I came here;

06:36.870 --> 06:38.510
the first person I saw

06:39.190 --> 06:39.920
was you.

06:40.950 --> 06:41.920
Since then,

06:42.510 --> 06:44.950
I have believed in fate.

06:48.240 --> 06:49.190
What do you think?

06:49.190 --> 06:50.070
Surprised?

06:50.510 --> 06:52.570
Wang Jianhua is quite affectionate.

06:53.159 --> 06:55.159
He might have been sincere at first.

06:55.630 --> 06:56.390
But later,

06:57.120 --> 06:58.920
he probably just craved

06:59.310 --> 07:01.170
the satisfaction he got from you.

07:06.800 --> 07:07.530
Tell me then.

07:07.870 --> 07:08.390
I was

07:08.390 --> 07:10.120
a girl as poor as a church mouse,

07:10.160 --> 07:10.800
with no degree

07:10.800 --> 07:11.720
and no job.

07:13.040 --> 07:13.830
As for him,

07:14.120 --> 07:15.920
Once his father was reinstated,

07:16.270 --> 07:18.730
he'd be
a university professor's son again.

07:19.240 --> 07:20.570
What did he want from me?

07:20.750 --> 07:22.080
How nice you were to him.

07:22.800 --> 07:24.260
He wanted your sincerity.

07:24.560 --> 07:25.160
He wanted your willingness

07:25.160 --> 07:26.820
to help him however you could.

07:27.920 --> 07:28.600
He was never

07:28.600 --> 07:29.600
a good person to begin with.

07:29.600 --> 07:31.260
And he had even less hope here.

07:31.600 --> 07:32.390
It was your devotion

07:32.390 --> 07:33.600
that made him feel

07:33.920 --> 07:34.920
he still had value

07:35.270 --> 07:36.870
and was still worthy of love.

07:39.390 --> 07:40.430
Zhou Cheng

07:41.070 --> 07:42.159
understood this,

07:43.060 --> 07:44.560
but that silly girl who ran into a tree

07:44.560 --> 07:45.750
didn't.

07:47.070 --> 07:48.000
Her devotion

07:48.230 --> 07:50.090
didn't earn her the same respect.

07:50.560 --> 07:52.510
It only built up a mediocre man's

07:52.730 --> 07:54.000
false confidence.

07:56.830 --> 07:57.480
Why...

07:57.800 --> 07:59.930
Wh-Why are you looking at me like that?

08:01.040 --> 08:02.000
It takes a man

08:02.600 --> 08:03.680
to know a man.

08:04.560 --> 08:05.070
Xiaolan,

08:05.070 --> 08:06.270
don't joke like that.

08:06.510 --> 08:07.160
I hate people

08:07.160 --> 08:08.820
like Wang Jianhua the most...

08:08.950 --> 08:09.920
Keep it down.

08:11.190 --> 08:11.800
Sit, sit.

08:12.310 --> 08:14.040
I won't joke like that anymore.

08:17.870 --> 08:18.470
By the way,

08:19.270 --> 08:20.130
why do you think

08:20.830 --> 08:21.560
Xia Ziyu

08:21.640 --> 08:23.310
wants you back in the Xia family?

08:23.310 --> 08:25.510
Isn't she afraid you'll cause trouble?

08:25.600 --> 08:26.390
She thinks

08:27.560 --> 08:28.270
I'm still that silly girl

08:28.270 --> 08:29.360
from before.

08:30.040 --> 08:31.570
Enthusiastic, impulsive,

08:31.600 --> 08:33.059
acting without thinking.

08:33.510 --> 08:34.240
She probably feels that

08:34.240 --> 08:35.700
if I stay in the Xia family,

08:36.000 --> 08:37.460
she can control me better.

08:38.000 --> 08:39.260
With so many eyes on me,

08:40.240 --> 08:41.240
it'd be hard for me

08:41.360 --> 08:42.630
to steal her thunder.

08:47.040 --> 08:48.240
What a rotten person.

08:51.840 --> 08:53.870
Every time you talk about yourself,

08:54.150 --> 08:55.080
it feels like

08:55.080 --> 08:57.080
you're talking about someone else.

08:57.240 --> 08:58.260
Because

08:59.790 --> 09:01.080
for me, those things

09:01.510 --> 09:02.440
are long past.

09:04.120 --> 09:05.480
I don't want to live

09:06.000 --> 09:07.320
in a fog like before.

09:07.870 --> 09:08.960
I want to start over

09:09.630 --> 09:11.230
and live life to the fullest.

09:13.960 --> 09:14.560
Well said.

09:17.030 --> 09:18.320
Seeing Xia Ziyu today,

09:19.390 --> 09:20.240
she clearly has so many

09:20.240 --> 09:21.040
dark thoughts

09:21.240 --> 09:22.970
and has done such shady things.

09:23.390 --> 09:24.840
Yet on the surface, she pretends

09:24.840 --> 09:25.900
to be kind and weak.

09:26.910 --> 09:28.200
She backed down today,

09:28.790 --> 09:30.030
but who knows what dirty tricks

09:30.030 --> 09:31.600
she'll have in the future.

09:31.840 --> 09:32.470
Yeah.

09:33.510 --> 09:34.970
Even a tiny fly is annoying

09:35.480 --> 09:36.320
if it keeps

09:36.910 --> 09:37.840
buzzing around.

09:40.200 --> 09:40.790
Xiaolan,

09:42.030 --> 09:43.360
my school is collecting

09:43.510 --> 09:45.170
desired major applications.

09:45.200 --> 09:46.030
I plan

09:47.390 --> 09:48.120
to study law.

09:53.150 --> 09:54.390
What I want to say is,

09:55.200 --> 09:56.240
no matter how

09:56.480 --> 09:57.630
Xia Ziyu provokes you,

09:57.630 --> 09:58.760
don't be impulsive.

09:59.150 --> 10:00.320
Don't think about using violence

10:00.320 --> 10:01.380
to solve problems.

10:01.670 --> 10:02.670
Trust the law.

10:03.030 --> 10:04.960
Protect yourself and your family.

10:07.390 --> 10:08.550
I know. Thank you.

10:14.750 --> 10:16.000
You're so young,

10:16.960 --> 10:18.760
yet you've been through so much.

10:19.720 --> 10:20.580
Are you afraid?

10:22.960 --> 10:23.480
Afraid?

10:24.790 --> 10:25.720
Maybe not.

10:26.910 --> 10:27.960
I just don't want

10:29.790 --> 10:31.120
to worry these people.

10:35.380 --> 10:36.240
I'm not afraid.

10:44.010 --> 10:46.410
[Spring, 1984]

10:53.000 --> 10:57.420
♪ Blow, blow, let the wind blow ♪

10:57.450 --> 11:02.850
♪ Wipe away the glistening tears
in your eyes ♪

11:02.880 --> 11:07.160
♪ Blow, blow, let the wind blow ♪

11:03.510 --> 11:04.840
Great!

11:05.600 --> 11:06.550
Come here.

11:06.790 --> 11:07.960
Blue Phoenix Clothing Store

11:07.390 --> 11:13.980
♪ Take away all the sadness;
no matter who it is in the wind ♪

11:08.080 --> 11:09.870
is officially open today!

11:10.240 --> 11:11.960
1, 2, 3!

11:11.510 --> 11:13.020
[Blue Phoenix]

11:14.160 --> 11:14.870
Great!

11:14.870 --> 11:16.200
There's a grand opening sale:

11:16.200 --> 11:17.750
everything is 10% off,

11:17.870 --> 11:19.120
and 20% off for 2 pieces and above.

11:19.120 --> 11:19.910
Spend enough to get

11:19.910 --> 11:21.600
free gifts like scarves.

11:21.790 --> 11:23.000
Welcome to shop!

11:23.000 --> 11:23.360
Great!

11:23.360 --> 11:24.360
Welcome!

11:24.390 --> 11:25.030
Welcome!

11:26.030 --> 11:27.000
Take a look, everyone.

11:27.000 --> 11:28.120
Great prices!

11:28.440 --> 11:29.510
Affordable clothes,

11:29.510 --> 11:29.960
and very stylish!

11:29.960 --> 11:30.870
These are all new.

11:30.870 --> 11:32.030
Fresh from the warehouse.

11:32.030 --> 11:33.290
Take a look, everyone.

11:37.440 --> 11:38.360
This outfit is the trendiest

11:38.360 --> 11:39.690
in Longcheng right now.

11:40.270 --> 11:41.200
How much is this?

11:41.630 --> 11:42.960
Let me check.

11:44.520 --> 11:45.320
Yes?

11:45.320 --> 11:46.240
Can you

11:46.240 --> 11:47.510
get this in my size?

11:47.750 --> 11:48.680
This one, right?

11:48.720 --> 11:49.150
Yes.

11:50.150 --> 11:51.840
This should fit.

11:52.840 --> 11:53.630
I quite like it.

11:53.630 --> 11:55.870
But my thighs are a bit thick.

11:56.080 --> 11:57.870
Do you think I should pair it with a skirt

11:57.870 --> 11:59.000
or pants?

12:00.840 --> 12:01.600
Pants.

12:02.630 --> 12:03.440
Pants...

12:03.480 --> 12:04.280
What's wrong?

12:04.790 --> 12:06.600
I have thick legs.

12:06.600 --> 12:08.110
I don't know if it'd go with a skirt...

12:08.110 --> 12:08.480
Miss,

12:08.480 --> 12:09.750
your legs aren't thick at all.

12:09.750 --> 12:10.320
I think skirts

12:10.320 --> 12:11.360
and pants both suit you.

12:11.360 --> 12:12.860
If you're really self-conscious,

12:12.860 --> 12:14.150
you can get a skirt.

12:14.480 --> 12:15.440
As for skirts,

12:15.550 --> 12:17.030
this one actually goes well with it.

12:17.030 --> 12:17.600
But...

12:17.960 --> 12:18.600
I think

12:18.960 --> 12:20.000
pants work too.

12:20.120 --> 12:20.720
Look here.

12:21.150 --> 12:22.000
We have these

12:22.480 --> 12:23.320
jeans.

12:23.550 --> 12:24.480
They're high-waisted.

12:24.480 --> 12:25.750
They'll definitely make you look slim.

12:25.750 --> 12:26.600
You can try them all on.

12:26.600 --> 12:27.960
If you don't like them, no pressure.

12:27.960 --> 12:29.030
If you like them, buy them all.

12:29.030 --> 12:29.480
Okay.

12:29.480 --> 12:30.360
I'll try them all.

12:30.360 --> 12:30.760
Right.

12:30.840 --> 12:32.080
The fitting room is over there.

12:32.080 --> 12:32.470
Okay.

12:32.510 --> 12:33.370
Take your time.

12:35.270 --> 12:35.910
Xiaolan,

12:36.550 --> 12:37.120
I...

12:37.320 --> 12:38.000
It's okay.

12:38.240 --> 12:39.550
Mom, don't be nervous.

12:40.790 --> 12:42.250
Ma'am, come here for a sec.

12:42.390 --> 12:42.850
Coming.

12:43.930 --> 12:44.550
Do you have

12:44.550 --> 12:45.480
another size for this shirt?

12:45.480 --> 12:46.840
Let me check for you.

12:58.750 --> 12:59.840
Shopping for clothes?

12:59.840 --> 13:01.550
Your outfit looks pretty good.

13:01.550 --> 13:03.080
No, mine's pretty nice too.

13:03.440 --> 13:04.100
Let's chat!

13:04.390 --> 13:04.910
Hey!

13:05.200 --> 13:06.200
No fun.

13:16.000 --> 13:16.550
Fen.

13:16.990 --> 13:17.910
Stop working so hard.

13:17.910 --> 13:18.960
There are no customers anyway.

13:18.960 --> 13:19.690
Take a break.

13:20.390 --> 13:21.790
Styling is my weak point.

13:21.790 --> 13:23.030
I need to study and practice more.

13:23.030 --> 13:24.630
Just in case someone comes in.

13:24.630 --> 13:25.150
Fen.

13:25.600 --> 13:26.030
Look.

13:26.480 --> 13:27.340
Those two guys,

13:27.720 --> 13:29.120
they just squat by our door.

13:29.120 --> 13:30.850
The customers dare not come in.

13:31.000 --> 13:32.750
Business used to be good.

13:33.270 --> 13:34.600
Are they intentionally

13:34.630 --> 13:35.560
messing with us?

13:36.030 --> 13:36.930
-Ladies.
-Hey, pretty.

13:36.930 --> 13:37.840
Came to buy some clothes?

13:37.840 --> 13:38.790
Wanna grab a bite?

13:38.790 --> 13:39.650
Don't run away!

13:39.670 --> 13:40.960
Look, you scared them away.

13:40.960 --> 13:41.620
Seriously.

13:41.790 --> 13:43.670
Ma'am, hope business is booming.

13:47.280 --> 13:48.280
Dirty hooligans.

13:58.320 --> 13:59.000
Pretty lady,

13:59.000 --> 14:00.200
looking for clothes?

14:00.790 --> 14:01.510
Don't go.

14:02.150 --> 14:03.550
Wanna go on a date?

14:03.720 --> 14:04.150
Look,

14:04.320 --> 14:05.750
you scared them away.

14:07.480 --> 14:07.960
Bro,

14:08.630 --> 14:09.670
this job is great.

14:10.320 --> 14:11.720
We can just bask in the sun,

14:11.720 --> 14:12.650
check out girls,

14:13.030 --> 14:14.430
and make some easy money.

14:15.510 --> 14:17.170
How much longer can we do this?

14:18.440 --> 14:19.270
Our boss said,

14:19.510 --> 14:21.000
as long as she doesn't say stop,

14:21.000 --> 14:22.840
we can do this every day.

14:26.960 --> 14:27.720
What are you doing?

14:27.720 --> 14:28.520
Are you crazy?

14:28.790 --> 14:30.030
-What are you doing?
-Tossing water and cleaning.

14:30.030 --> 14:31.600
It's my responsibility
to keep my storefront clean.

14:31.600 --> 14:32.790
Do I need your permission

14:32.790 --> 14:34.120
to clean my storefront?

14:34.720 --> 14:35.630
You wench.

14:36.120 --> 14:37.720
You did that on purpose, didn't you?

14:37.720 --> 14:38.670
Just you wait.

14:38.960 --> 14:39.960
Wait for what?

14:42.120 --> 14:43.550
Are you going to get the police

14:43.550 --> 14:44.880
or the security patrol?

14:45.320 --> 14:46.910
I'll be waiting right here.

14:47.100 --> 14:48.600
I can't wait

14:48.600 --> 14:50.120
to have a chat with the police

14:50.120 --> 14:51.720
about vagrants

14:51.960 --> 14:54.270
disturbing private businesses.

14:54.480 --> 14:55.680
It's a serious issue.

14:56.120 --> 14:57.240
You wanna die?

14:57.870 --> 14:58.670
I'll kill you.

14:59.120 --> 14:59.480
What are you doing?

14:59.480 --> 15:01.080
Let's talk this over nicely.

15:02.360 --> 15:04.290
What do you two think you're doing?

15:04.870 --> 15:05.360
Drinking...

15:05.360 --> 15:06.390
We... We're just...

15:06.390 --> 15:07.030
passing by. Just passing by.

15:07.030 --> 15:08.160
Finished drinking?

15:09.270 --> 15:10.630
Are you three ladies all right?

15:10.630 --> 15:11.290
We're fine.

15:11.360 --> 15:12.340
If you have any trouble in the future,

15:12.340 --> 15:13.550
remember to call the police.

15:13.550 --> 15:13.910
Okay.

15:14.030 --> 15:15.390
Thank you.

15:15.670 --> 15:16.870
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

15:19.600 --> 15:20.270
It's okay.

15:20.360 --> 15:21.090
Don't worry.

15:21.600 --> 15:22.240
Let's go.

15:22.510 --> 15:23.360
Seriously.

15:30.790 --> 15:31.320
Fen,

15:31.840 --> 15:32.750
Shangdu

15:33.080 --> 15:34.600
is a provincial capital after all.

15:34.600 --> 15:36.120
We're strangers there.

15:36.770 --> 15:37.720
What if...

15:37.750 --> 15:38.360
Fengmei,

15:39.080 --> 15:39.790
I know,

15:40.550 --> 15:41.510
you're afraid those people

15:41.510 --> 15:42.390
will come back for revenge.

15:42.390 --> 15:43.360
Exactly.

15:44.080 --> 15:44.600
Look,

15:44.840 --> 15:45.870
we drove those

15:45.870 --> 15:47.130
hooligans away today.

15:47.200 --> 15:48.550
But what if they come back

15:48.550 --> 15:49.960
and try something else,

15:50.240 --> 15:51.750
or play dirty tricks on us?

15:52.360 --> 15:54.360
I get scared just thinking about it.

15:55.150 --> 15:56.280
They wouldn't dare.

15:56.880 --> 15:57.640
Those two men

15:57.670 --> 15:59.530
obviously took someone's money.

15:59.840 --> 16:02.240
They'll only do
as much as they're paid for.

16:02.720 --> 16:03.480
Even if they really

16:03.480 --> 16:04.470
dare to try anything,

16:04.470 --> 16:05.200
that's perfect.

16:05.200 --> 16:07.270
The police can catch them red-handed.

16:07.270 --> 16:09.200
But those cowards in the Xia family

16:09.240 --> 16:10.200
probably only have the guts to pull

16:10.200 --> 16:11.260
some dirty tricks.

16:11.270 --> 16:13.480
The Xia family sent those two?

16:15.200 --> 16:16.200
It must be them.

16:16.960 --> 16:17.750
Only they

16:18.000 --> 16:19.530
would want to see my demise.

16:20.840 --> 16:21.840
But don't worry.

16:22.080 --> 16:22.810
I have a plan.

16:23.510 --> 16:24.670
In a few days,

16:24.870 --> 16:27.400
they won't have time
to play all these tricks.

16:41.550 --> 16:43.510
Two bowls of rice with toppings!

16:45.150 --> 16:47.350
Free refills on rice if it's not enough!

16:47.390 --> 16:48.520
Thanks, Mrs. Huang.

16:48.720 --> 16:49.320
Auntie,

16:49.670 --> 16:50.390
here's the money.

16:50.390 --> 16:51.000
All right!

16:51.910 --> 16:52.550
How did you come up with

16:52.550 --> 16:53.550
making this rice with toppings?

16:53.550 --> 16:54.910
I've never seen it before.

16:54.910 --> 16:56.630
Business hasn't been great,

16:56.790 --> 16:58.120
so I just came up with it myself.

16:58.120 --> 16:58.720
Is it good?

16:58.750 --> 16:59.350
It's good.

16:59.670 --> 17:00.720
Come back often if you like it.

17:00.720 --> 17:01.240
Sure.

17:01.960 --> 17:02.390
Here.

17:02.960 --> 17:03.360
Okay.

17:03.360 --> 17:04.270
This is really delicious.

17:04.270 --> 17:04.800
Isn't it?

17:05.030 --> 17:06.480
Come back often if you like it!

17:06.480 --> 17:07.240
Take care!

17:09.640 --> 17:10.720
Xiaolan, you're here.

17:10.720 --> 17:11.640
Come, sit.

17:12.640 --> 17:13.480
Have a seat.

17:14.000 --> 17:14.599
Come here.

17:14.790 --> 17:15.650
Let me tell you.

17:16.000 --> 17:16.530
Xiaolan.

17:16.750 --> 17:19.000
This rice dish you taught me to make,

17:19.200 --> 17:20.640
everyone loves it.

17:21.270 --> 17:22.440
From now on, when you come here,

17:22.440 --> 17:23.829
it's on the house. All free.

17:23.829 --> 17:24.790
I couldn't do that.

17:24.790 --> 17:25.680
Running a business isn't easy.

17:25.680 --> 17:26.790
You have to charge me.

17:26.790 --> 17:27.680
Don't say that.

17:27.680 --> 17:29.160
You made my shop so popular.

17:29.160 --> 17:30.560
I can't thank you enough.

17:30.960 --> 17:31.620
Mrs. Huang.

17:31.880 --> 17:32.690
Check, please.

17:32.690 --> 17:33.110
Coming.

17:33.110 --> 17:34.170
It's settled then.

17:34.440 --> 17:35.480
Coming!

17:43.230 --> 17:46.310
[Price List]

17:55.510 --> 17:56.160
Hongxia!

17:57.720 --> 17:59.920
Come here, I need to tell you something.

18:06.960 --> 18:07.640
What is it?

18:08.310 --> 18:09.440
Look, our business

18:09.440 --> 18:10.700
isn't doing very well.

18:11.070 --> 18:12.350
Hasn't your mother been saying

18:12.350 --> 18:14.080
she wants to find you a husband?

18:15.920 --> 18:16.750
Why don't you take

18:16.750 --> 18:17.880
this time to go back,

18:18.000 --> 18:19.240
help out at home,

18:19.480 --> 18:20.830
and learn some skills?

18:21.480 --> 18:22.960
You don't know how to do anything.

18:22.960 --> 18:23.960
When you get married,

18:23.960 --> 18:25.090
you'll get scolded.

18:25.880 --> 18:27.680
I'm doing this for your own good.

18:27.680 --> 18:28.240
You know?

18:29.380 --> 18:30.320
You mean

18:30.350 --> 18:31.000
you don't want me

18:31.000 --> 18:32.070
to work here anymore?

18:32.070 --> 18:32.310
No—

18:32.310 --> 18:33.000
What about her?

18:33.000 --> 18:34.600
Why don't you make her leave?

18:34.790 --> 18:36.310
Watch your mouth.

18:36.310 --> 18:37.510
Keep your voice down.

18:40.160 --> 18:41.620
That's my sister-in-law.

18:41.780 --> 18:43.350
The shop belongs to her.

18:43.650 --> 18:44.440
She's the boss.

18:44.440 --> 18:45.770
How can I make her leave?

18:47.550 --> 18:48.590
Hey! It's all...

18:48.830 --> 18:50.160
All gone! Seriously!

18:51.400 --> 18:52.000
Ma'am,

18:52.390 --> 18:53.250
I'm not stupid.

18:53.550 --> 18:54.400
I know the boss of this shop—

18:54.400 --> 18:55.330
Xia Changzheng!

18:56.480 --> 18:57.480
Get the hell out!

18:58.160 --> 18:59.030
Who are you?

19:00.830 --> 19:01.960
Have you forgotten?

19:01.960 --> 19:03.440
It's your bro Zhao Yong.

19:05.070 --> 19:06.030
I'm not looking for you.

19:06.030 --> 19:07.160
We're looking for her.

19:07.160 --> 19:08.290
She knows who we are.

19:09.070 --> 19:09.480
I...

19:09.480 --> 19:11.160
Hurry up and pay us the money

19:11.160 --> 19:12.070
for blocking the clothing store.

19:12.070 --> 19:13.000
Clothing store?

19:13.200 --> 19:13.590
What?

19:13.790 --> 19:14.750
It's an adult talk;

19:14.750 --> 19:15.640
none of a kid's business.

19:15.640 --> 19:16.240
Go inside.

19:16.480 --> 19:17.750
Hey, stop pointing, will you?

19:17.750 --> 19:18.790
What's wrong with pointing?

19:18.790 --> 19:19.400
Calm down,

19:19.830 --> 19:20.270
bro.

19:20.480 --> 19:21.750
This isn't my shop.

19:21.750 --> 19:22.720
Let's talk over there.

19:22.720 --> 19:24.200
Don't ruin their business.

19:24.200 --> 19:25.260
Fine, cut the crap.

19:25.680 --> 19:27.030
This was agreed upon beforehand.

19:27.030 --> 19:27.720
Pay up.

19:27.750 --> 19:29.070
You really think we're stupid, don't you?

19:29.070 --> 19:29.680
Stop pointing.

19:29.680 --> 19:31.350
Let me tell you, before taking the job,

19:31.350 --> 19:32.750
we already figured out

19:32.750 --> 19:33.480
your family's messy business.

19:33.480 --> 19:34.210
Understand?

19:34.400 --> 19:35.830
What do you mean "someone else's shop"?

19:35.830 --> 19:36.350
This is the shop

19:36.350 --> 19:37.720
you own with Xia Changzheng?

19:37.720 --> 19:38.200
Hey...

19:38.310 --> 19:39.030
Shut up!

19:41.030 --> 19:42.720
H-H-Hongbing.

19:43.720 --> 19:44.780
What are you doing?

19:45.480 --> 19:46.240
You've got a problem?

19:46.240 --> 19:47.110
I... I...

19:47.750 --> 19:48.350
Get lost.

19:49.350 --> 19:49.830
Uh...

19:50.070 --> 19:50.480
Scram!

19:51.000 --> 19:51.440
Hey!

19:51.920 --> 19:53.480
This really isn't our shop.

19:54.200 --> 19:55.200
Let's have a bowl of noodles too.

19:55.200 --> 19:55.550
Hey.

19:55.920 --> 19:56.680
Don't.

19:57.370 --> 19:57.900
Get lost!

19:57.920 --> 19:59.120
Calm down. Calm down.

19:59.240 --> 20:00.240
H-H-Have a drink.

20:00.590 --> 20:01.880
Don't, don't. How about this?

20:01.880 --> 20:03.200
I'll pour you some water, okay?

20:03.200 --> 20:03.720
What?

20:04.550 --> 20:05.610
What are you doing?

20:06.200 --> 20:07.350
When we paid for Xia Ziyu's

20:07.350 --> 20:08.500
schooling, we said

20:08.920 --> 20:10.200
we'd share the blessings

20:10.200 --> 20:11.480
and work together.

20:12.000 --> 20:13.000
But look at it now.

20:13.200 --> 20:14.920
They're making money themselves,

20:14.920 --> 20:16.230
living the high life.

20:16.480 --> 20:18.590
Yet they didn't even leave
any scraps for your niece!

20:18.590 --> 20:19.240
Exactly.

20:19.680 --> 20:21.070
It's simply too much.

20:21.960 --> 20:22.690
I'm going to look for your mother!

20:22.690 --> 20:23.720
-Mom.
-Get out of my way!

20:23.720 --> 20:24.960
-What are you doing?
-Mother!

20:24.960 --> 20:25.270
Mother!

20:25.270 --> 20:26.030
Mom is asleep.

20:26.030 --> 20:26.490
Mother!

20:26.590 --> 20:28.310
What's going on?

20:29.030 --> 20:29.400
Mother!

20:29.400 --> 20:31.350
You've been
rambling on in a panic for ages,

20:31.350 --> 20:33.080
but you haven't made any sense.

20:33.270 --> 20:34.830
Don't rush. Speak slowly.

20:35.270 --> 20:35.880
Mother.

20:36.200 --> 20:37.130
You have no idea.

20:37.270 --> 20:38.600
That eatery in the city,

20:38.720 --> 20:40.840
is run by Eldest Brother
and Sister-in-law.

20:40.840 --> 20:41.770
What did you say?

20:41.960 --> 20:43.110
They are the owners.

20:43.920 --> 20:44.480
Really?

20:45.920 --> 20:46.520
Hongbing!

20:46.830 --> 20:47.510
Xia Hongbing!

20:47.510 --> 20:48.110
Hongbing!

20:48.480 --> 20:50.000
Xia Hongbing, get over here!

20:50.000 --> 20:51.510
Hurry up.

20:54.720 --> 20:55.920
Is what she said true?

20:56.830 --> 20:58.510
I don't know if it's true or not.

20:58.510 --> 20:59.790
But I went to

21:00.160 --> 21:01.270
Eldest Sister-in-law's home village

21:01.270 --> 21:02.270
and asked around.

21:02.270 --> 21:03.530
Here is what they said.

21:04.160 --> 21:05.160
They said

21:05.440 --> 21:07.500
she is incredibly good to her family.

21:08.750 --> 21:10.150
She even pays them wages.

21:10.350 --> 21:11.480
Do you know how much?

21:11.550 --> 21:12.080
How much?

21:12.400 --> 21:13.800
It'll scare you to death.

21:14.310 --> 21:15.310
One hundred yuan!

21:15.790 --> 21:16.590
How much?

21:16.720 --> 21:19.720
And that's not counting
the New Year's red envelopes.

21:21.550 --> 21:22.070
My god.

21:22.790 --> 21:23.920
Is what he said true?

21:24.070 --> 21:24.920
It's true!

21:24.920 --> 21:25.310
Mother.

21:25.310 --> 21:26.440
This child doesn't lie.

21:26.440 --> 21:27.830
I've seen it several times myself,

21:27.830 --> 21:29.920
Aunt going to the bank to deposit money.

21:29.920 --> 21:31.350
A stack this thick.

21:31.510 --> 21:32.470
It's definitely this thick!

21:32.470 --> 21:33.800
Must be over a thousand.

21:34.030 --> 21:35.430
Isn't that infuriating?

21:36.510 --> 21:38.400
Where are they now?

21:39.110 --> 21:40.750
It seems like debt collectors

21:40.750 --> 21:41.510
are pestering them.

21:41.510 --> 21:42.310
-What?
-What?

21:43.160 --> 21:44.510
They are so rich now,

21:44.510 --> 21:46.350
yet people still come to collect debts?

21:46.350 --> 21:47.680
They are obviously playing

21:47.680 --> 21:48.610
the victim card.

21:48.750 --> 21:49.240
Mother.

21:49.360 --> 21:50.830
They are obviously fooling us.

21:50.830 --> 21:52.400
She's doing it just for you to see.

21:52.400 --> 21:53.660
Just putting on an act.

21:55.880 --> 21:56.590
You two,

21:56.590 --> 21:58.480
just go home and get the money.

21:58.480 --> 21:59.270
It's that simple.

21:59.270 --> 21:59.920
All right, all right.

21:59.920 --> 22:00.590
Dagang, Dayong.

22:00.590 --> 22:02.110
We are all bros from neighboring villages,

22:02.110 --> 22:02.590
aren't we?

22:02.590 --> 22:03.640
If you make a scene,

22:03.640 --> 22:04.970
others will laugh at us.

22:05.070 --> 22:05.830
That girl from No.1 High School,

22:05.830 --> 22:07.090
isn't she your family?

22:07.310 --> 22:08.070
Why aren't you afraid

22:08.070 --> 22:09.590
of your own family laughing at you?

22:09.590 --> 22:10.030
Hey.

22:10.240 --> 22:10.680
Hey...

22:11.000 --> 22:12.550
Bro, what are you saying?

22:12.880 --> 22:15.110
We are not that kind of people.

22:15.540 --> 22:17.070
Whether you two are that kind of people,

22:17.070 --> 22:17.920
don't you have a clue

22:17.920 --> 22:18.880
yourself?

22:19.240 --> 22:19.900
Haven't you

22:20.000 --> 22:21.590
seen our shop

22:21.590 --> 22:22.830
this afternoon?

22:23.400 --> 22:24.800
Business is really slow.

22:24.830 --> 22:26.090
If business were good,

22:26.240 --> 22:27.790
we would have just paid you.

22:28.160 --> 22:29.240
It's getting late.

22:29.240 --> 22:30.510
Following us around

22:30.590 --> 22:31.480
won't help.

22:31.480 --> 22:32.540
Just go back first.

22:33.210 --> 22:33.690
Fine.

22:33.720 --> 22:34.180
Then...

22:35.590 --> 22:36.450
how about this?

22:36.480 --> 22:37.080
One month.

22:38.790 --> 22:40.750
We'll definitely pay you two in a month.

22:40.750 --> 22:41.480
Is that okay?

22:41.880 --> 22:42.720
One week.

22:43.590 --> 22:44.550
Just one week.

22:44.680 --> 22:45.110
Hey!

22:45.200 --> 22:46.720
If I don't get the money in a week,

22:46.720 --> 22:48.000
I'll air all your family's

22:48.000 --> 22:49.510
dirty laundry.

22:50.400 --> 22:52.030
That girl from No.1 High School

22:52.030 --> 22:53.560
is more honest than you two.

22:54.270 --> 22:55.310
That's one week.

22:55.950 --> 22:57.000
If we don't see the money,

22:57.000 --> 22:57.680
we'll...

22:57.680 --> 22:58.270
No, no.

22:58.310 --> 22:59.960
You'll definitely see the money.

22:59.960 --> 23:01.790
I keep my word.

23:01.880 --> 23:03.270
I keep my word.

23:05.270 --> 23:05.680
Okay.

23:06.160 --> 23:07.760
-Keep your word.
-Thank you.

23:08.030 --> 23:08.480
Okay.

23:11.790 --> 23:12.850
What are you doing?

23:18.880 --> 23:19.880
Isn't that right?

23:19.920 --> 23:20.350
Exactly.

23:20.350 --> 23:20.830
Mom.

23:23.350 --> 23:24.680
The two heroes are back.

23:28.400 --> 23:30.440
You two are full of tricks.

23:32.010 --> 23:33.920
Tricking the whole family
into making money for you,

23:33.920 --> 23:34.480
right?

23:35.030 --> 23:37.070
Playing dirty tricks,
yet keeping it all to yourselves.

23:37.070 --> 23:38.830
You're so smooth at that.

23:39.430 --> 23:40.540
Let me tell you.

23:41.880 --> 23:42.810
I'm not dead yet.

23:43.350 --> 23:45.110
This family hasn't fallen apart.

23:45.110 --> 23:48.120
Every penny you earned before

23:49.030 --> 23:51.070
belongs to this family!

23:52.010 --> 23:52.970
You... You...

23:53.000 --> 23:54.150
From today on,

23:54.830 --> 23:55.550
this shop

23:56.100 --> 23:59.100
will be managed by you and Third's wife

23:59.200 --> 23:59.920
together.

24:06.010 --> 24:06.560
Look.

24:06.590 --> 24:09.070
Mom, what are you saying?

24:09.550 --> 24:11.550
Aren't we part of the Xia family?

24:12.070 --> 24:13.400
We listen to you.

24:13.830 --> 24:15.200
But what you just said,

24:15.200 --> 24:16.830
does that mean

24:17.270 --> 24:19.070
you want me to hand over the shop?

24:20.600 --> 24:21.120
Mom.

24:21.440 --> 24:22.830
If you're worried,

24:22.960 --> 24:24.680
let her keep the money with me.

24:24.680 --> 24:25.200
Wouldn't that be fine?

24:25.200 --> 24:26.460
Then you can rest easy.

24:26.590 --> 24:29.400
That's just moving it
from the left pocket to the right.

24:29.400 --> 24:30.030
No, no.

24:30.480 --> 24:31.640
The main thing is,

24:32.340 --> 24:33.830
what does the shop have to do

24:33.830 --> 24:35.230
with Hongbing's family?

24:36.000 --> 24:36.530
Besides,

24:36.830 --> 24:38.160
with all the farm work at home,

24:38.160 --> 24:39.960
are we supposed to stop doing it?

24:40.400 --> 24:40.880
Wait.

24:42.000 --> 24:43.800
Mom doesn't know the situation.

24:44.480 --> 24:46.240
We haven't made any money.

24:46.590 --> 24:47.960
How could we have any savings?

24:47.960 --> 24:48.720
Right, right.

24:48.720 --> 24:49.790
You know when we opened the shop,

24:49.790 --> 24:50.440
it was just...

24:50.440 --> 24:51.200
-We…
-We gave free things.

24:51.200 --> 24:52.270
-More or less.
-Yeah.

24:52.270 --> 24:52.680
Right.

24:52.680 --> 24:54.270
Look how much we gave away.

24:54.510 --> 24:55.640
If we had money,

24:55.720 --> 24:57.030
we would've sent Junbao

24:57.030 --> 24:58.640
to school in the county town long ago.

24:58.640 --> 24:59.040
Right?

25:00.880 --> 25:01.400
Mom.

25:02.350 --> 25:03.680
Actually, if you ask me,

25:04.180 --> 25:05.550
you're getting on in years,

25:05.550 --> 25:06.210
aren't you?

25:06.480 --> 25:07.680
We work the land in the village,

25:07.680 --> 25:09.410
but how much can we really earn?

25:09.510 --> 25:10.540
Why don't we all

25:10.880 --> 25:12.590
move to the county town together?

25:12.590 --> 25:13.110
Right?

25:13.880 --> 25:15.010
You can retire there

25:15.270 --> 25:16.750
and keep an eye on the shop.

25:16.960 --> 25:17.920
It would be great.

25:17.920 --> 25:18.400
Mother.

25:19.160 --> 25:20.960
I think Hongbing is right.

25:21.200 --> 25:23.070
Besides, life is much better in the city,

25:23.070 --> 25:23.720
isn't it?

25:23.920 --> 25:25.180
Let's move to the city.

25:25.750 --> 25:26.720
We're also responding to the national call

25:26.720 --> 25:28.850
for Reform and Opening-Up, aren't we?

25:29.270 --> 25:30.350
Let's

25:31.110 --> 25:32.240
discuss that later.

25:35.680 --> 25:36.750
Right now,

25:37.440 --> 25:39.170
the most important thing is...

25:41.030 --> 25:42.880
for you to hand over all the money

25:43.480 --> 25:45.080
you've earned immediately.

25:45.550 --> 25:46.350
Dismissed.

25:47.310 --> 25:48.030
But, Mom...

25:51.350 --> 25:52.000
Let's go.

25:52.350 --> 25:53.070
Go!

25:54.310 --> 25:55.370
What are you doing?

26:04.510 --> 26:05.240
Tsk?

26:05.480 --> 26:06.740
What's with the "tsk"?

26:06.960 --> 26:07.890
I'm telling you,

26:08.400 --> 26:10.130
if that money gets handed over,

26:10.160 --> 26:11.290
we're through.

26:11.550 --> 26:12.880
I'm going back to my parents'.

26:12.880 --> 26:14.200
What are you yelling about?

26:14.200 --> 26:14.640
What about it?

26:14.640 --> 26:15.840
Don't be like Liu Fen.

26:16.350 --> 26:17.110
Be like her?

26:17.550 --> 26:19.480
I think Liu Fen did the right thing!

26:20.110 --> 26:21.920
Xia Xiaolan was right.

26:22.510 --> 26:23.550
Your Xia family

26:23.750 --> 26:24.720
is a pit.

26:25.070 --> 26:25.850
A complete pit!

26:25.850 --> 26:26.510
Say that again.

26:26.510 --> 26:27.680
And what if I do?

26:27.680 --> 26:28.640
Say it again, and I'll slap you to death!

26:28.640 --> 26:30.350
Come on. Hit me!

26:30.510 --> 26:31.000
I will!

26:31.880 --> 26:32.740
Let me tell you,

26:33.030 --> 26:33.830
I'm not Xia Dajun,

26:33.830 --> 26:34.590
that coward.

26:52.310 --> 26:53.200
Take care, you two.

26:53.200 --> 26:53.830
Thank you.

26:53.960 --> 26:55.020
Please come again.

26:55.070 --> 26:55.680
Goodbye.

26:56.030 --> 26:56.460
Come in.

26:56.460 --> 26:57.090
Welcome.

26:57.350 --> 26:57.950
Come on in.

26:59.800 --> 27:00.640
Take care.

27:00.670 --> 27:01.730
Please come again.

27:01.920 --> 27:02.640
Goodbye.

27:02.830 --> 27:03.350
Thank you.

27:03.350 --> 27:04.880
This outfit is on a special sale.

27:04.880 --> 27:06.080
You have great taste.

27:06.110 --> 27:06.880
This one is

27:07.000 --> 27:08.240
the latest style in Longcheng.

27:08.240 --> 27:10.000
Our shop is the only place
that has it in Shangdu.

27:10.000 --> 27:10.750
No, no.

27:11.270 --> 27:12.510
Just do as you normally do.

27:12.510 --> 27:13.070
Doesn't it look good?

27:13.070 --> 27:13.920
It suits you perfectly.

27:13.920 --> 27:14.920
Look how beautiful it is.

27:14.920 --> 27:16.050
It really suits you.

27:16.270 --> 27:16.920
It's gorgeous.

27:16.920 --> 27:17.640
You want this?

27:17.640 --> 27:18.030
Yes.

27:18.200 --> 27:18.590
Okay.

27:18.750 --> 27:19.240
Then,

27:19.310 --> 27:20.070
I'll set it aside for you.

27:20.070 --> 27:20.440
Try it on.

27:20.440 --> 27:21.550
I think this one suits you better.

27:21.550 --> 27:22.000
Okay.

27:22.270 --> 27:23.240
Welcome.

27:23.270 --> 27:24.600
Take your time looking.

27:24.640 --> 27:26.700
Feel free to try on anything you like.

27:27.110 --> 27:27.640
Let's go.

27:32.880 --> 27:33.790
Welcome!

27:34.920 --> 27:35.790
Coming, coming.

27:35.790 --> 27:36.830
Welcome.

27:37.270 --> 27:38.510
Same as last time?

27:45.720 --> 27:46.270
Fen.

27:47.350 --> 27:48.270
What did you eat

27:48.270 --> 27:49.510
when you were pregnant?

27:49.510 --> 27:50.240
How did you make Xiaolan

27:50.240 --> 27:51.510
so smart?

27:51.920 --> 27:53.640
She's a natural at business.

27:54.200 --> 27:55.030
That friend she met

27:55.030 --> 27:55.880
in Longcheng

27:55.900 --> 27:56.790
is amazing.

27:57.350 --> 27:59.370
Those stockings
are in such high demand right now.

27:59.370 --> 28:01.240
There aren't many places in Shangdu
that have them.

28:01.240 --> 28:02.300
Several customers

28:02.480 --> 28:04.160
who only planned to buy one or two items,

28:04.160 --> 28:05.960
once they heard about the free stockings,

28:05.960 --> 28:07.160
bought several more.

28:07.350 --> 28:09.350
I think her friend's surname is Bai.

28:09.830 --> 28:10.720
I heard she

28:11.680 --> 28:13.030
helped Xiaolan a lot.

28:13.680 --> 28:14.160
Fen.

28:14.480 --> 28:15.000
There's something

28:15.000 --> 28:16.110
we need to discuss.

28:16.400 --> 28:18.060
Business is so good right now.

28:18.160 --> 28:19.220
In a couple of days,

28:19.580 --> 28:20.640
when Xiaolan takes her exams,

28:20.640 --> 28:21.770
will you go with her?

28:22.110 --> 28:23.910
I definitely have to go with her.

28:24.200 --> 28:25.270
I'm just worried you

28:25.270 --> 28:26.870
can't handle the shop alone.

28:26.880 --> 28:28.680
Then we'll just close for 3 days.

28:28.960 --> 28:29.350
Right.

28:29.350 --> 28:30.160
It's no big deal.

28:30.160 --> 28:31.200
Her exams are important.

28:31.200 --> 28:31.720
Right.

28:31.790 --> 28:33.160
Close for 3 days?

28:33.550 --> 28:34.680
That's shutting

28:34.680 --> 28:35.480
the money out.

28:35.920 --> 28:36.680
Xiaolan.

28:37.110 --> 28:38.310
It's such an important event.

28:38.310 --> 28:38.920
I can't possibly

28:38.920 --> 28:39.850
let you go alone.

28:40.000 --> 28:41.130
I have to be with you.

28:41.750 --> 28:42.960
Uncle will go with me.

28:43.350 --> 28:43.790
Mom.

28:44.070 --> 28:45.030
You and Auntie

28:45.030 --> 28:46.680
just stay here and run the shop.

28:46.680 --> 28:47.200
Besides,

28:47.200 --> 28:48.640
you can't go in when I'm taking the exam.

28:48.640 --> 28:49.750
You'd just be standing at the gate.

28:49.750 --> 28:50.640
You might as well

28:50.640 --> 28:52.370
earn more money for my tuition.

28:52.880 --> 28:53.960
How could I forget

28:53.960 --> 28:54.790
about your uncle?

28:54.790 --> 28:56.080
Let your uncle go with you.

28:56.080 --> 28:56.610
As for us,

28:56.640 --> 28:58.370
we'll stay here and make money.

29:15.510 --> 29:15.960
Here.

29:16.110 --> 29:16.640
Xiaolan.

29:17.240 --> 29:19.240
Eat this egg custard while it's hot.

29:20.070 --> 29:20.800
Thanks, Mom.

29:21.770 --> 29:23.570
Rest a bit before studying more.

29:24.160 --> 29:26.640
♪ Let my heart boil ♪

29:26.070 --> 29:26.550
Mom.

29:26.920 --> 29:27.830
It's okay, go to sleep.

29:27.590 --> 29:29.890
♪ Are you also the same? ♪

29:27.830 --> 29:29.000
You won't disturb me.

29:29.000 --> 29:29.550
I have unfinished work

29:29.550 --> 29:30.680
in the kitchen.

29:30.840 --> 29:32.590
I'll come back to sleep when I'm tired.

29:32.590 --> 29:36.800
♪ Dreams will always shine ♪

29:37.690 --> 29:40.200
♪ There may also be regrets ♪

29:40.230 --> 29:43.980
♪ If you lose something,
be strong ♪

29:44.350 --> 29:46.750
♪ And head to the distant place ♪

29:47.840 --> 29:50.370
♪ The dreams we dream in the daytime ♪

29:51.160 --> 29:53.760
♪ Are passionate yet naive ♪

29:54.400 --> 29:58.890
♪ Our youth ♪

29:56.270 --> 29:57.270
You must be hungry.

29:57.270 --> 29:58.530
Have something to eat.

29:59.380 --> 30:02.750
♪ Why don't we move forward
and never look back? ♪

29:59.480 --> 30:00.750
Keep your head up.

30:00.920 --> 30:02.180
You'll ruin your eyes.

30:02.780 --> 30:06.210
♪ Even if our youthful ambitions
are not fulfilled yet ♪

30:03.240 --> 30:04.550
Take a break every now and then.

30:03.890 --> 30:05.740
[Xia Xiaolan's way of memorizing words]

30:04.720 --> 30:05.830
Okay, got it.

30:06.420 --> 30:09.200
♪ We never give up ♪

30:09.820 --> 30:13.190
♪ We can rely on each other on the road,
and that's enough ♪

30:13.210 --> 30:16.370
♪ Go ahead smiling and never look back ♪

30:16.390 --> 30:19.750
♪ Don't look down on us youths
whose great ambitions are yet fulfilled ♪

30:19.940 --> 30:22.850
♪ The future will be amazing ♪

30:23.290 --> 30:26.450
♪ As long as we do our best ♪

30:26.670 --> 30:32.340
♪ That'd be enough ♪

30:27.880 --> 30:28.750
I've basically remembered

30:28.750 --> 30:30.480
how to solve all the problems now.

30:30.480 --> 30:31.280
That's great.

30:31.920 --> 30:32.750
I'm prepared.

30:49.960 --> 30:50.760
What's wrong?

30:51.070 --> 30:51.830
What are you thinking about?

30:51.830 --> 30:52.630
You zoned out.

30:53.030 --> 30:53.830
Nothing.

30:54.480 --> 30:55.720
You seem happy today.

30:55.720 --> 30:56.640
Of course!

30:57.480 --> 30:58.720
My dad got reinstated.

30:58.720 --> 30:59.310
Really?

31:00.000 --> 31:00.790
The decision just came down.

31:00.790 --> 31:02.830
He starts
at the Ministry of Education next week.

31:02.830 --> 31:03.400
Ziyu,

31:03.920 --> 31:04.520
our family

31:04.960 --> 31:07.350
has finally
made it through the hard times.

31:07.350 --> 31:07.960
Jianhua,

31:08.200 --> 31:09.110
let's find a time.

31:09.110 --> 31:10.640
I want to visit your parents

31:10.790 --> 31:12.650
and congratulate them in person.

31:13.920 --> 31:14.400
Sure.

31:15.030 --> 31:16.030
I might have to go

31:16.030 --> 31:17.590
tidy up the old house now.

31:18.030 --> 31:19.290
You stay here and read.

31:19.680 --> 31:21.140
Th-Then let me go with you.

31:23.200 --> 31:24.600
It's all physical labor.

31:24.680 --> 31:25.940
Girls can't handle it.

31:26.350 --> 31:27.350
I can do it myself.

31:27.480 --> 31:28.000
You,

31:28.070 --> 31:29.470
just stay here and study.

31:29.830 --> 31:31.360
The exam is more important.

31:32.240 --> 31:32.840
Good luck.

31:45.960 --> 31:47.160
First in the prelims?

31:48.070 --> 31:50.730
And she wants to
come to a college in the capital?

31:52.030 --> 31:53.270
Are you still not over

31:53.270 --> 31:54.160
Wang Jianhua?

31:57.510 --> 31:58.110
Next,

31:59.070 --> 31:59.920
we will award

31:59.920 --> 32:01.720
the top 3 students in the prelims

32:02.110 --> 32:04.030
scholarships and grants.

32:05.270 --> 32:07.000
Part of a student's good grades

32:07.160 --> 32:08.480
is thanks to the support

32:08.480 --> 32:09.680
and company of their parents.

32:09.680 --> 32:10.310
I suggest

32:10.780 --> 32:11.880
that this scholarship

32:11.880 --> 32:13.750
be collected by the parents.

32:13.960 --> 32:15.030
What do you say?

32:15.480 --> 32:16.720
Yes!

32:17.830 --> 32:19.440
Then I'll read the list.

32:21.790 --> 32:23.110
First place in the prelims,

32:23.110 --> 32:24.400
Xia Xiaolan.

32:26.200 --> 32:28.110
Xiaolan really did us proud.

32:28.680 --> 32:30.340
Is Xia Xiaolan's parent here?

32:31.240 --> 32:32.240
Here! We're here!

32:33.030 --> 32:33.710
Not me.

32:34.750 --> 32:36.160
Liu Fen, they're calling you.

32:36.160 --> 32:37.880
-Please come to the stage.
-Xiaolan's parent.

32:37.880 --> 32:38.900
Go get the money, quick!

32:38.900 --> 32:39.760
So many people.

32:40.070 --> 32:41.200
Go on.

32:41.510 --> 32:43.350
We wish we could go up there.

32:51.110 --> 32:51.830
Great!

32:51.830 --> 32:52.830
Don't be nervous.

33:05.030 --> 33:06.090
Congratulations.

33:06.730 --> 33:07.720
Thank you, Principal.

33:07.720 --> 33:08.320
Thank you.

33:12.680 --> 33:13.610
Comrade Liu Fen,

33:14.510 --> 33:15.440
it's truly wonderful

33:15.440 --> 33:16.700
that you raised a child

33:16.750 --> 33:17.810
as good as Xiaolan.

33:17.920 --> 33:18.350
Come,

33:18.880 --> 33:19.740
say a few words.

33:19.790 --> 33:21.160
Give the other students and parents

33:21.160 --> 33:21.760
a pep talk.

33:22.010 --> 33:23.560
No, I'd rather not.

33:23.590 --> 33:24.510
Say a few words.

33:24.790 --> 33:25.400
Mom!

33:26.270 --> 33:27.070
Be confident!

33:27.270 --> 33:28.870
Confidence makes you shine.

33:30.680 --> 33:31.140
Come on.

33:33.810 --> 33:37.080
[All the best to the students of Anqing No.1 High School
for the National College Entrance Examination]

33:37.720 --> 33:38.720
Hello, everyone.

33:39.640 --> 33:41.240
I am Xia Xiaolan's mother,

33:42.030 --> 33:43.070
Liu Fen.

33:43.920 --> 33:44.350
Great!

33:48.070 --> 33:49.510
With the school right across the street,

33:49.510 --> 33:50.550
business is quite good.

33:50.550 --> 33:52.210
Students all come here to eat.

33:52.310 --> 33:53.200
It's a prime location.

33:53.200 --> 33:53.720
Okay.

33:54.200 --> 33:55.310
All right. I'll think about it.

33:55.310 --> 33:56.240
If you're interested,

33:56.240 --> 33:57.070
the rent is negotiable.

33:57.070 --> 33:58.200
Okay.

33:58.220 --> 33:59.820
What is there to think about?

34:00.480 --> 34:01.080
All right.

34:01.830 --> 34:02.830
You two saw it.

34:03.510 --> 34:04.770
This is the situation.

34:05.750 --> 34:06.400
We can't run

34:06.400 --> 34:07.470
this shop anymore.

34:08.159 --> 34:10.000
We have to transfer it sooner or later.

34:10.000 --> 34:10.929
When you go back,

34:11.190 --> 34:11.590
Dajun,

34:11.590 --> 34:12.920
tell Mom what you saw.

34:13.590 --> 34:14.920
She trusts you the most.

34:17.230 --> 34:17.880
Brother,

34:18.489 --> 34:19.969
you think Dajun is naive,

34:20.000 --> 34:21.860
so you want him to fool Mom, right?

34:22.440 --> 34:23.920
Anyway, before I left,

34:23.920 --> 34:25.090
Mom gave instructions.

34:25.090 --> 34:27.219
She sent me specifically to watch you.

34:27.320 --> 34:28.230
She knows you two

34:28.230 --> 34:29.360
like to play tricks.

34:29.800 --> 34:30.760
From now on,

34:30.880 --> 34:31.940
every penny earned

34:32.030 --> 34:33.159
must be handed over.

34:34.360 --> 34:35.290
What did she say?

34:35.440 --> 34:37.000
She said we play tricks?

34:37.610 --> 34:38.679
Is there anyone in our family

34:38.679 --> 34:39.760
dumber than us?

34:40.480 --> 34:41.920
Besides, do you think transferring a shop

34:41.920 --> 34:43.190
is like selling cabbages?

34:43.190 --> 34:45.190
How many people asked this morning?

34:45.800 --> 34:47.000
Dajun, you were here.

34:47.480 --> 34:48.510
Did anyone ask?

34:50.540 --> 34:51.440
Congratulations to you both.

34:51.440 --> 34:52.070
Thank you.

34:52.070 --> 34:53.330
Thank you, Principal.

34:54.030 --> 34:55.000
Chen Qing!

34:58.550 --> 35:01.150
Strive to go forward
without fear of hardship,

35:01.480 --> 35:03.880
succeed in the exams
and bring glory to all!

35:04.630 --> 35:05.280
Students,

35:06.030 --> 35:08.030
the college entrance exam
is in a few days.

35:08.030 --> 35:09.490
Do you have the confidence

35:09.630 --> 35:11.760
to take on the college entrance exams?

35:11.760 --> 35:14.360
-Yes, yes!
-Yes, yes!

35:17.910 --> 35:19.710
Why is it so lively in the school?

35:20.510 --> 35:21.920
It's 3 days from

35:21.920 --> 35:23.480
the college entrance exams.

35:23.480 --> 35:24.800
They're holding a meeting.

35:24.800 --> 35:27.340
Apparently, they notified
the parents and students

35:27.340 --> 35:28.550
to all come and participate.

35:28.550 --> 35:30.760
I heard the top students
who did well in the exams

35:30.760 --> 35:31.920
will even get money.

35:32.230 --> 35:32.920
Money?

35:33.030 --> 35:33.920
Yeah.

35:34.000 --> 35:34.860
How much money?

35:35.320 --> 35:36.720
Must be several hundred.

35:38.070 --> 35:39.670
Xia Xiaolan says her grades are good.

35:39.670 --> 35:41.130
She'll definitely get it.

35:41.600 --> 35:42.480
Right, Dajun.

35:42.510 --> 35:44.400
You... You didn't know about this?

35:44.400 --> 35:46.320
You should be participating in it.

35:46.320 --> 35:47.550
Didn't they notify you?

35:47.550 --> 35:48.350
Yeah, that...

35:48.760 --> 35:49.820
That shouldn't be.

35:49.920 --> 35:51.210
-You…
-That shouldn't be it.

35:51.210 --> 35:52.230
Yeah, you're her father.

35:52.230 --> 35:53.190
She didn't tell you

35:53.190 --> 35:54.370
something this important?

35:54.370 --> 35:54.970
Yeah.

35:55.030 --> 35:56.310
This... This kid...

35:56.670 --> 35:58.240
Our Ziyu would never do this.

35:58.240 --> 35:59.590
That's right, definitely not.

35:59.590 --> 36:00.400
Seriously.

36:04.000 --> 36:04.670
I forgot.

36:05.000 --> 36:06.230
Jianyong from the next village

36:06.230 --> 36:07.150
made an appointment for this afternoon

36:07.150 --> 36:08.070
to come see our house.

36:08.070 --> 36:09.130
Go, go, go quickly.

36:09.220 --> 36:09.920
Don't delay things.

36:09.920 --> 36:11.360
You guys sit here.

36:19.920 --> 36:20.510
Fen.

36:20.730 --> 36:22.730
Not only is your daughter amazing,

36:22.760 --> 36:24.820
you as her mother are remarkable too.

36:24.880 --> 36:25.760
I was so moved

36:25.760 --> 36:27.280
by what you said.

36:27.280 --> 36:28.150
My legs went weak.

36:28.150 --> 36:28.760
I don't even know

36:28.760 --> 36:29.710
what I was saying.

36:29.710 --> 36:30.480
That was so scary.

36:30.480 --> 36:31.740
I couldn't tell at all.

36:31.960 --> 36:33.020
Xiaolan's parent.

36:33.280 --> 36:33.920
Hello.

36:34.000 --> 36:35.230
Please don't rush off yet.

36:35.230 --> 36:36.000
Mr. Sun invited you

36:36.000 --> 36:37.000
to his office.

36:38.870 --> 36:39.910
The principal wants to see me?

36:39.910 --> 36:40.580
Yes.

36:41.160 --> 36:42.090
Then go quickly.

36:42.290 --> 36:43.280
I'll tell Xiaolan.

36:43.280 --> 36:44.840
We'll wait for you at the eatery.

36:44.840 --> 36:45.190
Okay.

36:45.400 --> 36:45.760
Go ahead.

36:45.760 --> 36:46.290
Let's go.

36:47.630 --> 36:48.630
Must be good news.

36:49.840 --> 36:53.060
[Anqing No.1 High School]

36:51.550 --> 36:52.610
Comrade, comrade.

36:52.760 --> 36:53.670
Who are you looking for?

36:53.670 --> 36:55.070
I'm looking for Xia Xiaolan.

36:55.070 --> 36:56.400
What is your relationship to her?

36:56.400 --> 36:57.260
I'm her father.

36:57.590 --> 37:00.120
I haven't heard that
Xia Xiaolan has a father.

37:00.650 --> 37:01.650
Watch your mouth!

37:01.760 --> 37:02.770
I told your mom

37:03.110 --> 37:05.000
we'd be at the eatery
in front of the school gate.

37:05.000 --> 37:06.000
She knows, right?

37:06.000 --> 37:06.440
Yes.

37:06.880 --> 37:07.610
That's good.

37:08.760 --> 37:09.760
Watch your mouth!

37:09.800 --> 37:11.000
You still can't go in.

37:11.070 --> 37:12.600
Wait, what is he doing here?

37:14.000 --> 37:14.530
Xiaolan!

37:14.910 --> 37:16.590
That's my daughter right there.

37:16.590 --> 37:17.120
Xiaolan!

37:17.550 --> 37:18.210
Move aside.

37:18.360 --> 37:19.000
Xia Dajun.

37:19.630 --> 37:20.700
What are you doing here?

37:20.700 --> 37:21.630
I am your father.

37:21.800 --> 37:23.110
Can't I come to see you?

37:24.150 --> 37:26.030
You have the nerve
to call yourself her father?

37:26.030 --> 37:27.560
Look at how you treated her.

37:27.880 --> 37:28.840
Shameless!

37:30.560 --> 37:32.070
I heard there's a meeting inside.

37:32.070 --> 37:33.280
All the parents are in there.

37:33.280 --> 37:34.360
I'm your father.

37:34.560 --> 37:35.710
Why didn't you invite me?

37:35.710 --> 37:36.310
Xia Dajun,

37:36.760 --> 37:38.020
what are you thinking?

37:38.440 --> 37:39.630
You want to be my father?

37:39.630 --> 37:40.630
Do you deserve to?

37:41.280 --> 37:43.030
You weren't there when I was suffering.

37:43.030 --> 37:44.440
Now that the hard times are over,

37:44.440 --> 37:46.040
you want to reap the rewards?

37:46.360 --> 37:47.500
Dream on.

37:48.280 --> 37:49.280
Usually, you don't even remember

37:49.280 --> 37:50.320
that I exist.

37:51.880 --> 37:53.340
I don't even need to guess.

37:53.670 --> 37:55.600
Xia Ziyu sent you here, didn't she?

37:55.910 --> 37:56.790
Ziyu said

37:57.420 --> 37:58.710
taking you and your mother back

37:58.710 --> 37:59.910
would be good for you.

38:01.090 --> 38:02.730
Ziyu said, Ziyu said.

38:03.070 --> 38:03.800
Xia Dajun.

38:04.230 --> 38:05.070
Can't you,

38:05.070 --> 38:05.760
just for once,

38:05.760 --> 38:07.090
use your brain to think?

38:07.840 --> 38:08.900
Look for yourself.

38:09.000 --> 38:10.030
Am I better off now,

38:10.030 --> 38:11.360
or when I was in the Xia family?

38:11.360 --> 38:12.150
Is there anyone in that family

38:12.150 --> 38:12.820
who wants the best for me

38:12.820 --> 38:13.820
or my mother?

38:14.670 --> 38:15.320
Dajun.

38:16.150 --> 38:16.760
Dajun.

38:18.110 --> 38:18.640
Xiaolan.

38:19.130 --> 38:20.280
Well, whatever needs to be said,

38:20.280 --> 38:21.230
let's talk at home.

38:21.230 --> 38:22.550
There are too many people here.

38:22.550 --> 38:23.320
Let's go home.

38:23.320 --> 38:24.680
Talk behind closed doors.

38:24.680 --> 38:25.360
Right, Brother?

38:25.360 --> 38:25.840
Yes.

38:26.070 --> 38:26.960
Xiaolan, d-don't

38:26.960 --> 38:28.150
talk here. Let's go home.

38:28.150 --> 38:29.630
Come on, go back with Auntie.

38:29.630 --> 38:30.670
What does this have to do with you?

38:30.670 --> 38:31.960
You haven't finished
your act yet, have you?

38:31.960 --> 38:32.470
Xiaolan.

38:32.470 --> 38:34.480
You're never done playing along, are you?

38:34.480 --> 38:34.920
Fine.

38:35.230 --> 38:36.800
Since the Xia family loves acting so much,

38:36.800 --> 38:37.400
all right,

38:37.480 --> 38:39.360
put on a good show right here today.

38:39.360 --> 38:40.320
With so many teachers

38:40.320 --> 38:41.360
and students here,

38:41.360 --> 38:42.670
go ahead and put on your act.

38:42.670 --> 38:43.550
Just act out

38:44.030 --> 38:46.160
how the Xia family plotted against me,

38:46.550 --> 38:47.110
and now,

38:47.110 --> 38:48.370
how you want to ruin me.

38:49.000 --> 38:49.800
I heard you

38:49.800 --> 38:51.760
are still living
at your older brother's house.

38:51.760 --> 38:53.690
Is there anyone else in that house?

38:54.590 --> 38:56.000
We can arrange for someone

38:56.000 --> 38:57.150
to accompany her for the exam.

38:57.150 --> 38:58.800
If you have trouble
with the travel expenses,

38:58.800 --> 38:59.510
I personally...

38:59.510 --> 39:00.640
No need, Principal.

39:01.030 --> 39:02.800
We'll handle the money ourselves.

39:02.800 --> 39:03.960
Thank you, Principal.

39:03.960 --> 39:04.510
Thank you.

39:04.510 --> 39:06.070
Mr. Sun! Mr. Sun!

39:08.320 --> 39:09.000
Qi.

39:09.630 --> 39:11.030
Why are you so flustered?

39:11.440 --> 39:13.000
Xiaolan's father is here.

39:17.960 --> 39:18.890
What's going on?

39:19.030 --> 39:20.110
We are all your elders.

39:20.110 --> 39:21.030
You're

39:21.030 --> 39:22.360
so rude now.

39:22.360 --> 39:23.840
We all want what's best for you.

39:23.840 --> 39:24.500
Apologize!

39:25.120 --> 39:27.380
Who should apologize to whom, Xia Dajun?

39:27.550 --> 39:29.000
You kept claiming

39:29.000 --> 39:30.000
to be her father just now.

39:30.000 --> 39:31.110
What kind of father

39:31.330 --> 39:32.590
sides with outsiders?

39:32.590 --> 39:34.150
Shouldn't you side with your own daughter?

39:34.150 --> 39:34.880
Am I right?

39:35.070 --> 39:37.360
-Exactly.
-Yeah. Right.

39:37.440 --> 39:39.100
How can there be such a person?

39:39.880 --> 39:40.440
Yeah.

39:41.840 --> 39:42.970
Xia... Xia Xiaolan.

39:43.400 --> 39:44.200
Let me ask you.

39:44.580 --> 39:45.830
Am I your father?

39:45.920 --> 39:47.780
Are you coming back with me or not?

39:47.840 --> 39:48.440
You?

39:49.190 --> 39:50.230
Who do you think you are?

39:50.230 --> 39:50.840
You... You...

39:50.840 --> 39:51.700
Say that again.

39:51.710 --> 39:53.040
Fine, I'll say it again.

39:53.320 --> 39:54.150
Who do you think you are?

39:54.150 --> 39:55.410
Want me to say it again?

39:55.550 --> 39:56.030
I...

39:56.510 --> 39:57.480
What are you saying?

39:57.480 --> 39:58.320
Xia Dajun!

39:58.360 --> 39:59.110
I should teach you a lesson!

39:59.110 --> 40:00.110
Stop! Stop it!

40:00.630 --> 40:01.360
Liu Fen!

40:01.840 --> 40:02.550
Well said!

40:04.320 --> 40:05.000
Xia Dajun.

40:06.710 --> 40:07.710
I want a divorce.

40:08.880 --> 40:09.630
Divorce?

40:13.510 --> 40:14.840
What are you talking about?

40:14.840 --> 40:15.700
Say that again.

40:16.330 --> 40:17.300
Are you deaf?

40:17.710 --> 40:19.110
Didn't you hear Xiaolan?

40:19.440 --> 40:20.770
She didn't do anything.

40:21.550 --> 40:22.880
Yet others bullied her,

40:23.190 --> 40:25.190
and the Xia family
wants to drive her to death.

40:25.190 --> 40:26.630
You didn't stand up for her.

40:26.630 --> 40:27.420
Instead, you joined outsiders

40:27.420 --> 40:28.500
to pressure her.

40:30.000 --> 40:32.190
You don't deserve to be Xiaolan's father.

40:32.190 --> 40:33.050
Let me tell you,

40:33.360 --> 40:35.230
Xiaolan is not going back
to the Xia family.

40:35.230 --> 40:36.690
I'm not going back either.

40:36.760 --> 40:37.800
I want a divorce.

40:38.630 --> 40:39.280
Liu Fen.

40:39.800 --> 40:40.590
With so many people here,

40:40.590 --> 40:41.360
aren't you ashamed

40:41.360 --> 40:42.620
of saying such things?

40:42.630 --> 40:44.430
What's shameful about divorce?

40:44.550 --> 40:45.280
Everyone has the right

40:45.280 --> 40:46.670
to pursue happiness.

40:47.230 --> 40:47.710
Right.

40:48.110 --> 40:49.510
Divorce isn't shameful.

40:50.590 --> 40:52.250
Xia Dajun is the shameful one.

40:53.510 --> 40:54.070
Liu Fen.

40:54.630 --> 40:55.960
Who gave you the guts?

40:56.720 --> 40:57.670
You mother and daughter

40:57.670 --> 40:59.200
are truly a pair of bitches.

40:59.480 --> 41:00.800
Today, in front of everyone,

41:00.800 --> 41:02.130
I'll teach you a lesson!

41:03.230 --> 41:04.290
Comrade, comrade!

41:15.440 --> 41:17.030
I'm telling you, Xia Dajun.

41:17.030 --> 41:17.960
I'll teach you a lesson today!

41:17.960 --> 41:18.690
You bastard!

41:34.070 --> 41:34.840
Get off!

41:35.630 --> 41:36.190
Stop!

41:36.630 --> 41:37.690
Stop it, all of you!

41:39.920 --> 41:40.920
Don't step on me.

41:42.670 --> 41:43.200
Xiaolan!

41:43.590 --> 41:44.000
Xiaolan.

41:44.000 --> 41:44.920
Xiaolan! Xiaolan!

41:44.920 --> 41:46.070
How are you, Xiaolan?

41:46.070 --> 41:47.510
Where did you hurt yourself?

41:47.510 --> 41:48.070
Mom.

41:49.070 --> 41:50.510
I think my hand hurts.

41:50.590 --> 41:51.280
Your hand?

41:51.280 --> 41:52.710
Ms. Qi. Send her to the hospital.

41:52.710 --> 41:53.070
Okay.

41:53.070 --> 41:53.510
Hurry!

41:53.510 --> 41:54.070
Be careful.

41:54.070 --> 41:54.960
Slowly.

41:55.510 --> 41:56.670
Okay, let's go.

41:56.760 --> 41:57.630
Hurry up!

41:58.360 --> 41:59.420
Make way! Make way!

41:59.480 --> 41:59.880
Hurry!

42:11.190 --> 42:12.400
Looking at the X-ray,

42:12.400 --> 42:13.880
there is no major fracture.

42:13.880 --> 42:15.550
But there is a hairline fracture.

42:15.550 --> 42:16.210
Right here.

42:17.920 --> 42:19.320
She shouldn't move it for a while.

42:19.320 --> 42:19.760
Okay?

42:20.400 --> 42:22.000
We need to put a cast on it.

42:23.710 --> 42:24.280
Well...

42:24.840 --> 42:26.400
Can she still write?

42:26.840 --> 42:28.280
The college entrance exam
is in a few days.

42:28.280 --> 42:30.140
She was 1st in our city's prelims.

42:30.360 --> 42:31.750
This exam is very important to her.

42:31.750 --> 42:33.110
You have to help us.

42:33.550 --> 42:34.750
First in the prelims?

42:36.000 --> 42:37.930
To take the exam for 3 days in the row

42:38.000 --> 42:39.600
will ruin her wrist for good.

42:41.280 --> 42:41.920
Dajun.

42:58.740 --> 43:00.540
For her to have such an accident,

43:00.630 --> 43:01.760
it really is a pity.

43:04.550 --> 43:05.480
It's all my fault.
